Package: ggpackets
Title: Package multiple ggplot layers for easier portability and modularization
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Doug", "Kelkhoff", email = "kelkhoff.douglas@gene.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create groups of ggplot layers that can be easily migrated from
  one plot to another, reducing redundant code and improving the ability to format
  many plots that draw from the same source ggpk layers.
Depends:
  R (>= 3.1.0)
LazyData: true
